_sText:
The plot of this de map is that the terrorists have infiltrated an American nuclear research center and are trying to cause mass panic among American's be creating a nuclear catastrophy. The counter terrorists must protect the new "prototype" long range nuclear fusion missile and the fusion power supply for the base.

This map will be BETA tested on server #1 of www.theserverspot.com
If you have any suggestions you can look for my post about this map on their forums or you can pm me on csbanana. All custom textures are compiled into the bsp using the all mighty packrat.
